    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get a taste of managing your own laundry store in this Demo version of Laundry Store Simulator! In this demo you will be able to play the opening sections of the game. There's no limit of how long you can play the demo, but available features and your progression are limited compared to the full game. Your progress and save data from the demo <strong>can not</strong> be transferred to the full version of the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to own the world's best laundry store? Transform a small laundry shop into a laundry empire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the following features in Laundry Store Simulator:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/66d4db01232ed1e0885aaf53ed9eb998.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Build a small laundry store into a thriving business empire! Upgrade your equipment, design and expand your store, hire staff, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/ef953b48268f06c8467c4b47a0c1cf8c.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/b2cc5ffe361ff570d74453c6c02d112a.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Upgrade your equipment to provide exceptional cleaning services! Invest in high-quality washing machines, dryers, ironing equipment, and even automated washing machines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/284829a4413dc13002762ce305c93cf0.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/7dca6a108f4175afa1f93452cc6d45a7.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Create a stylish and inviting space to attract customers! Provide comfortable seating, warm decorations, and more funsies to welcome your customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/4be0a6e0333ce34bafc6bb29b8d5f857.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/e93d2fdc769d6f07a2fb870f73fdde78.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Grow your laundry business by unlocking new areas and features, offering complimentary services to attract more customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/ed2bf3314e85f35a5f74e5715ef07c3f.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/e0b8e3e8c97e7398ace596001b87a56f.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Build a dedicated team to manage your laundry store efficiently! Hire qualified and experienced staff laundry attendants, such as, washers, dryers, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/9dadc12254071798c0b7773d5f32dbf4.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/3bb8610d6482e1524b5bd43a260ee00d.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Boost your profits by selling cleaning supplies and becoming a one-stop shop for laundry needs! Offer a variety of cleaning products, including detergents, fabric softeners, stain removers, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/dec238a72832e3a145251a3d777cab23.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/f2922762fa9eb85d98d7b7750d48d626.avif?t=1731082716\" width=600 height=89 /></span>Offer convenient home delivery to build a loyal customer base! Optimize delivery routes for efficiency and cost-effectiveness and provide excellent customer service during the delivery process!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/cf33f8237a87baacb5ae5e6af6718173.poster.avif?t=1731082716\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/cf33f8237a87baacb5ae5e6af6718173.webm?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239280/extras/cf33f8237a87baacb5ae5e6af6718173.mp4?t=1731082716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
